    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "「すみません、今お電話大丈夫でしょうか」\nもちろん……っと。お、すぐにきたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I'm sorry‚ is it okay to call you now?\"\nOf course… and‚ she replied quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　琴乃、どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Kotono‚ what's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0832213085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.9922461034
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.9922461034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、みんなといる時に……月ストを思いきり\nバッシングしてる動画を観ちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Earlier‚ when I was with everyone…\nI watched a video where Moon Tempest was heavily criticized.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6089127701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.0422427973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "頭の中がぐるぐるして、どうしたらいいか分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My head started spinning‚ and I didn't know what to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0422427973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.108909464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それで……みんなに何も言わずに\n自分の部屋に戻ってきちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… without saying anything to anyone‚\nI went back to my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.308909464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今は落ち着いてるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you feeling calm now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.108909464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.1006814322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきよりは大丈夫ですけど……\nでも、まだ……胸がキュッと締め付けられてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm better than earlier‚ but…\nStill‚ my chest feels tight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4006814322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.0006860098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに心配をかけて申し訳ないです\nでも、どうしたらいいか分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for worrying everyone.\nBut I didn't know what to do‚ so I thought…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4673526765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それで……{user}さんになら\n相談出来るかもって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "maybe I can talk to you‚\n{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8673592886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.36735878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この間、俺が言ったことをちゃんと覚えてて\nくれて嬉しいよ。電話してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad you remembered what I said the other day\nand called me. Thank you for calling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333456676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……もう、なんで{user}さんは\nそんなに優しいんですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚\nWhy are you so kind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6354297321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.1666732788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n私、どうしたら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nWhat should I do――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7354292234,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1564.5810763000013,
          "startTime": 84.3000102997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.3020958901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "っ……はい。さくら……？\n今は……ダメ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah. Sakura-chan…?\nNot now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7687625568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃？　どうした？　ノックの音が聞こえたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono? What happened? I heard a knock‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1020943642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3597.9122478999984,
          "startTime": 96.7000066121
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5397.912247899995,
          "startTime": 98.5000066121
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.7193198046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょ、さくら――きゃあっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ w-wait‚ Sakura-chan— Aaah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7193198046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 100.7333309175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし……琴乃？　どうした！？\nダメだ……通話が切れてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… Kotono? What's wrong!?\nNo… the call got disconnected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8666637422,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6000.00915519999,
          "startTime": 111.8666728974
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、琴乃からメッセージが届いてるな\n「すみません、少しだけ待って下さい」……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there's a message from Kotono.\n\"I'm sorry‚ please wait for a moment\"… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4999970755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8999935151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.9666601818
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.9666601818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　さっきは驚かせてしまってごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? I'm sorry for startling you earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8501735529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.1168412369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "さくらが無理矢理部屋に入って来たから、驚いて\n切っちゃいました。今はダメって言ったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan came into my room forcefully‚ so I had to hang up.\nI told her it's not a good time now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6835079035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.3501745702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なんにせよ、無事で良かったよ\nそれにしても、さくらはどうしてそんなことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I'm glad that you're okay.\nBut why did Sakura do something like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3666601818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.0455190501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、私を誘いたかったらしくて\n明日……さくらととんかつデートに行って来ます",
      "translations": {
